Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,DISPATCH — Emergency Response Modernization. From 9-1-1 to units\Nrolling in under 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.14,0:00:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,LOGCOM ERMP challenge — Installation Incident Response. Real-time\Ntranscription, AI triage, geospatial unit orchestration.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Five synthetic 9-1-1 calls. We pick the structure fire in base housing\N— Magnolia Loop, family unaccounted for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stage 1: live call transcript streams in. Whisper-style segmentation,\Ndispatcher and caller separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stage 2: AI triage agent. Structured-output JSON — incident type, APCO\Nseverity ECHO, recommended units, callback questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:01:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stage 3: geospatial orchestration. Engines, rescue, ambulance routed\Nfrom the nearest station, ETA computed live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And the dispatcher CAD entry — incident summary, unit assignment,\Nscene safety brief — drafted by the Kamiwaza-deployed model.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.71,0:01:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,DISPATCH — runs inside your accredited environment. Kamiwaza Stack.\NDeploy in hours, not months.
